ss="t me29 x23 h35 yfd5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The article by Ellen G. White </div><div class="t m5e0 x9f h35 yf51 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which follows this lesson was </div><div class="t m6f3 x9f h35 yc85 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">printed in the </div><div class="t mcdb xef h35 ya9a ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Review and Her-</div><div class="t m9fc x9f h35 ye03 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ald, </div><div class="t m373 x4c h35 ybbf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">September 18, 1893. &quot;Now </div><div class="t m58f x9f h35 y1213 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Is the Time to Dedicate All to </div><div class="t m206 x9f h35 y759 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&quot; is to be read as supple-</div><div class="t m14e9 x9f h35 y678 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mentary material with this </div><div class="t m3f5 x9f h35 yd31 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">week&apos;s lesson. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
